  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_055_000015",
    "sentence": "考之載籍之可徵者，著《輿服篇》，冠諸《儀衛》之首。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_055_000016",
