        "label": "ORG"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_055_000017",
    "sentence": "隨水草遷徙，則有氈車，任載有大車，婦人乘馬，亦有小車，貴富者加之華飾。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_055_000018",
    "sentence": "禁制疏闊，貴適用而已。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_055_000019",
    "sentence": "帝後加隆，勢固然也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_055_000020",
    "sentence": "輯其可知著於篇。",
    "entities": []
  },
