    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_055_000029",
    "sentence": "此其遺意歟？",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_055_000030",
    "sentence": "送終車，車樓純飾以錦，螭頭以銀，下縣鐸，後垂大氈，駕以牛。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
